


𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝘁𝗼 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗲 𝗰𝗼𝗱𝗲𝗶𝗻𝗲 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝗹𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲 𝘁𝗮𝗯𝗹𝗲𝘁𝘀 𝗼𝗳 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗰𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗺𝗼𝗹
step 1. crush up 20g of paracetamol tablets and dissolve them in 100ml of water.
step 2. add 50 ml of diethyl ether (i'll add the SAFEST WAY of getting this to its finest level in purity in the next message) to the mixture and shake it vigorously for five minutes.
step 3. let the mixture sit for 30 minutes so that the diethyl ether can separate the chemicals
step 4. once the layers have separated, use an eyedropper or syringe to move the diethyl ether layer to a new container (it'll be the only liquid in there or you can just use a strainer if you're lazy)
step 5. add a small amount of hydrochloric acid (you can find this as muriatic acid in a hardware store) to the diethyl ether and shake the mixture for five minutes.
step 6. let it sit for 30 minutes again, then transfer ONLY THE HYDROCHLORIC ACID LAYER IN THE MIXTURE YOU CURRENTLY HAVE ON YOU to a new container using the eyedropper or syringe
step 7. add a small amount of sodium hydroxide (lye) to the hydrochloric acid and shake it for five minutes.
step 8. let it sit for 30 minutes again
step 9. transfer the top layer to a new container
step 10. evaporate the liquid using a hot plate and you'll be left with pure codeine

𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝘀𝗮𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘄𝗮𝘆 𝗼𝗳 𝗴𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗱𝗶𝗲𝘁𝗵𝘆𝗹 𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗲𝗿
step 1. take hand sanitizer
step 2. put it on top of a coffee filter or a strainer with very small holes in it
step 3. once its on top of the thing you're using to filter it, cover it in iodized table salt but don't add too much
step 4. let the mixture seep down through the filter and underneath the filter it'll start dripping the liquid which is pure diethyl ether



